PrecisReappointment of SHEILA LEGGETT of Calgary, Alberta, as a member of the National Energy Board to hold office during good behaviour, effective September 27, 2013 and ending on December 31, 2013; and designation of SHEILA LEGGETT of Calgary, Alberta, member of the National Energy Board, as Vice-Chairperson of the National Energy Board, effective September 27, 2013 and ending on December 31, 2013.
